\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did she make wine or medicine or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No, you see - you - you'd - no you'd no need.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Or brew beer?
