I know. Well all women in them days were harder workers than men. No, but they - for instance I mean to say, they brought all them children up, they did all washing, did all cleaning of th'house, did all cooking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 And yet they went without the food?
