And then if there was going anybody without then it's - it's - it's her as goes short then, in them days. She'd make sacrifice. But I mean, honestly, the women really are not the weaker sex. It's - it's a - it's a misnomer. An
d on top of that the male is softer. The lady can stand a lot more pain without moaning and groaning and telling everybody.
