\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Could you leave food on your plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes. Yes. Oh yes. If I'm full I'm full do you see. Me mother weren't like a woman like that. She didn't make me }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 eat}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  because she'd put it out on plate.
