\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No. He wanted to be drinking pints.
