They - they didn't - they didn't seem to bother but - as a little boy I can remember playing in kitchen and getting some cardboards and cutting 'em all out like so much a time and giving these 'ere cardboards to me pals an
d - I were going to be a - a Shakespearean actor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Do you remember the things they stressed as right and wrong for you to learn though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What I consider important is - is for each man and woman do unto others as they like to be done to. I remember
 one fellow as come working up Co-op and he said - get at top if I have to - he said, I'll get at top and I don't care who I hurt and I don't care who I climb over. I don't like them people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Was this what your parents considered important too, that you do onto others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
Yes. Yes. That's right, yes, yes, it's - it's no - it's no good - you don't get no benefit, you getting a couple of shilling more than anybody else especially when you've done a - when you done it - when you got it under that circum
stances. No. It's not - cast they bread upon the waters and it will return to thee after many days. But how? No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Are you a religious person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Not altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you go to church as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes, I went New Jerusalem. That's a new - th
at's the new church. They reckon to be that you'll - be the same in heaven as what you are here. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did your mum and dad go too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well when they were younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 The New Jerusalem, it's a new church, is it church of England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No. It's called New Jerusalem New Church. They - they're what they call Swedenborgians - life after death. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Tell me about it when you were a boy, what it was like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh well see I mean to say - I told you - I told you on there that the - they wouldn't h
ave a boys brigade, they'd have a - ambulance brigade, because they don't believe in fighting. But it - they'll attend to the sick.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 When you were a child were you told to hit back if someone hurt you, did you fight then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh I - I've always fough
t for myself. I've always fought for myself like that because me mother - she were busy, me father played piano 'til - I were what you called a loner. See I mean when you're a longer it's just like you - just like your parents being in a public house and 
you were their daughter. When the show commences they've no time for you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you feel this a lot as a boy, that your parents hadn't a lot of time to spend with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well we never used to play with all boys. Yes, but I'm just telling you about th
e pub business. You - you have to do best you can now and - you might be unlucky. You might fall. You see. Or you might be lucky and go to some - there 'ere clubs and that and - keep all right but - eventually - through it you come to be a loner. See, you
r parents are inside there and their - they'll not let you - mix with anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 They didn't let you in the pub at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh no, no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You had to keep out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh yes. No. No, you - you just like - just like shutting door like - shutting
 that door and you - you're in now. No, you - you - you got it in for do for yourself. You - you've time on your hands. Now you can go wrong with time on your hands. And eventually, if you don't - if you don't get out and get to some club or something lik
e that you'll get that you'll be a loner and when it comes to mixing with people to talk to them you'll not be able to enter in conversation. You have got - you have got - learnt that through being a loner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How did you spend your Saturdays then when you were a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 I used to go and watching Wanderers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Always?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
Always. Sometimes I used to go out to Millbank and - when I went on canal bank I could smoke cigarettes without anybody seeing me. - Yes, that's what you used to do, everybody did it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How did you spend your Sundays when you were a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 At - at Sunday school. Yes.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Were you allowed to play games, would your parents let you play games or anything or did they think it was wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh yes, oh yes, they was - they let me play games, they weren't so bad I could - play games at Sunday. Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did both your mother and father attend the New Jerusalem?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well they did - you know, before they got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 . But - after than like I told you - mother were very busy and - me father he played piano more times than not and drunk. Well he couldn't go could he.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 But you went to Sunday school every Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes. At New }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 Jerusalem}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you go on Sunday school outings or picnics or things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No, w
e - we didn't go on outing, we - our big day were - Whitsuntide you know when - used to get your bun and coffee and - run for prizes. You know. Oh aye, run for prizes. Yes.
