Well no, I was too young at the time. No, they had for t'others. Tennis, you know, table tennis. Then they'd have a football team. Just like they have today. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did they have a temperance club?
