\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What did they think about it though, were they keen on swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well - well, as I tell you, they'd not much time for me. They were so busy they'd not much time for me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 So you really brought yourself up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 That's right. As I told you all these children in these public houses, they'd have to bring themselves up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Were you allowed to join in when adults were talking or were you told to keep quiet while adults were talking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well I weren't allowed to join in because - I didn't know what they were 
talking about. No - oh they would have - they said I were cheeky or something liked that if I talked, they'd soon stop that game.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Suppose you did something wrong, who punished you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well do you know, me mother and father, although me father drunk and that, they - they never hit us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You don't remember being punished at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
No. No. No. When I played wag all that time she didn't say anything, just said, here, when are you going to start going to school? No more. Never - never hit - they never hit me.
\par 
