\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 And you got a present did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes, just same yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 It wasn't a special day at home wi
th having a pub? Were you able to make Christmas Day a special day at home with your mother having a shop and a pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh yes, oh yes, you had your own - do what you want, anytime you could do what you want.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did she open the shop on Christmas Day though, she'd open the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well - well you see, in them days shops were nearly open all time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 So would Christmas Day be any different?
