 like he got onto stage do you see. Now he gets onto stage, he stands up and starts making all sorts of things with his back and - you know posin
g and one thing another. Now Bulldog were a different kind of wrestler than that. Bulldog says, bring him on. And he'll throw him out. I know one - well, I - I said - how's Bulldog going on with Terrible Turk today? Oh he says, they had him, he says, he b
roke his arm - just then. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did the women go and watch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
Well I couldn't tell you whether ladies but - but - they do - they used to go watch - they used - they used to go watch them all - in wrestlers at Turton Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
Oh - it's now - any - any - any hold you want. That - ladies used to go watching that and do you know what they used - they used to have a bucket with a - bucket of water in you know to throw on 'em like that and one time when they win somebody }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 shouts}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 , you, pull his hair mate and hit 'em with wheat end.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What's a wheat end?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Wheat. Wheat end. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Were these ordinary working men or were they professionals?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh - oh yes, they worked. They - they couldn't get the big money as Cassius }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 
Clay}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
 is getting you know and them lot, they couldn't get that big money. No, they worked and this 'ere Bulldog, when he wanted to put weight on, he used to drink a lot of water. For put weight on. Used to drink a lot of water.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did the ordinary colliers round Farnworth wrestle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh - oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Or was it just people who wrestled for money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No - they - biggest part of wrestlers really they were colliers, bit rough, aye. Yes.
