 instance - I - see like - the - the lady of the house now, we'll say, supposing her husband in pit, he strained his back. In them days they used to get some fish called }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 ray}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
