he'll tell me. What sort of girl, this thing and that. So now see I get information about her and if th'information isn't good I don't turn up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You let her down?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Let her down, no, I sack her. In them time - in them days, every girl you got, didn
't mater if she worked in weaver or in - doff or cut like that - every time, will you - where you working? She's dressmaker. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 They\rquote re}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  all dressmakers. 'Til you found out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 They always said they were dressmakers - why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Aye. Well it - it were a better job than saying they were - they were mucky daughters. Or weavers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did your parents want you to be in at a certain time when you were at work?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did they want to know where you were going or want you to bring your friends home, meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No, no, they never bothered about that. I tell you - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 Farnworth}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  Co-op used take us on half days picnic every year. And this time we go to Blackpool and - and dancing in Blackpool in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 Tower}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  and with me is a fellow called Simmons. Now he's only }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
 like last week do you see. So - trains due out at half past ten. Twenty-five }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 past ten}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
 I says, hey, Alice com on else us be getting - whatsname. But no, we had to stop with these two ladies. He said, I'm having these lancers. So I thought to myself, well, you only got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
 last week. I've no ties. I can stop. So we stopped. So these ladies come back, we're up to station and we heard that whistle go - ooooh, and they're lights going out of station. Aye. We're in Blackpool now, these ladies 
went - these ladies went off home. So - sleeping there and having our breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 So you stayed the night in Blackpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes. So we stayed the night in Blackpool. No it's over to Tom White's in Grasmere Street and we asked him we said, hey has any
body caught our train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 And your parents didn't mind you were out all night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No. They just went over and asked, him said, hey did anybody caught your train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How old were you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14436562\charrsid9517149 when}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  you got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Twenty - twenty-six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Where did you meet your wife, tell me all about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh - I - I met her - at a dance. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You used to go dancing when you were younger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Where did your wife come from, was she a Bolton girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 ay}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
, she come from - whatsname - Tongue - Tongue Noor. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you have to save up to get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No, with having had some money left me through me grandfather - yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 I had money to start with. At that particular time if you'd sixty pound - in 1915, you could get houseful of furniture.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did your parents help you to set up home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh no, no, I'd - I'd money of me own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How long were you engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well - she were twenty-three. I - when I - when I - when I were going with her I'd be about - had I turned twenty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 She was older than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 I were older than her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You started going with her when you were twenty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you have a honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Aye, Blackpool. Yes. So -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 A big wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh no. No. See we'
re in pub. We're in pub and - her mother hadn't the money for to do a spread and my parents hadn't the time. When - when the pubs open the show commences and you -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you have no guests at your wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Lets see - like best - best man and that you know. I'd have about six and then went off. You - can't - there no -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you get a lot of presents in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh yes. Yes. Oh yes. The - somebody'd buy some }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736813\charrsid9517149 squeezers}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 , somebody'd buy you blankets and different things like that you know. Oh - oh yes, I got plenty of presents, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Where did you go to live after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 I lived up Tongue Hoor. Place called Scow}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 roft Street. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 That was still in Bolton wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Scowcroft Street, yes, up Tongue Moor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you live at that house a long time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well I lived there 'til about - 1924. Then 1924 I come up here. So I've been up here since 1924.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did your wife work when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes. She were a - I don't know - one of main jobs in't' - sp
inning place - I just forget what they call 'em. Not a doffer, higher up than that. Frame tenter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did she work after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 For a bit, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You still sent her out to work did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 I didn't send her out, no, didn't send her out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How did you feel about her working in those days, did men object to their wives working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No. No, no, not if wife wanted to work, see. But like, she - her health weren't all that good then do you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did she like her job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes, oh yes, yes. See really when you as a lady, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 , comes to be - you're going to have a bit of a rough time because, you see, your husband has to go to work. So what he does, he goes to work, locks you in - maybe neighbours all right next door, he gives th
em a knock and says, hey will you give me wife a - make her a pudding for her dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you do this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes. They all had to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What sort of illness did she have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well I couldn't tell you really, like I think it were kind of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 anemia}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  or something like that you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How did you go on about housekeeping in those days if she was working and you were working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh well - yes, yes. Oh well, there were bad times, he used - he used to take his share out - he used to - he used to see 
his - he used to have his share and should you have any children, as them children grew up and got a job and got to bring some wage in, he took a little bit more off you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What happened in your case, did you discuss the housekeeping and how the money should be spent at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
No. You just give it to her and - what she had left she kind of saved. See, for new things whenever we - when you got so much money you'd buy something extra. Do you see?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You didn't sort of work out how much housekeeping she should have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
Oh no. No, no. No, you can't do that. You can't do that. See, you might buy all different this week and different prices, you know what I mean. You don't just buy to a set scale. Sometimes you do treat yourself, don't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You didn't follow the Lancashire tradition of bringing your packet in and giving it to her and letting her decide?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
Yes, I used give her a packet. Yes, yes. Oh yes, I used to giver her a packet, yes. I think - I used to think it were only right. Yes. Then she'd give me what I could have. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Didn't you mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh no. No, she weren't bad. No. I know there were people like that. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 
For instance I mean like when I were in Scowcroft Street here, a fellow called - Falace, now he worked on coal and he a 
little drunken beggar and sometimes when he's coming home, street you know, rolling home, and if there were a lady walking at back of him he'd stop. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
He'd say, you, woman - I don't have women walking behind me. Get to front. Aye. I don't know. He wouldn't - he said he wouldn't have a woman walking behind him when he was drunk. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 I wonder why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How many rooms were there in the house in Scowcroft Street and how did you use them, Did you live on your own or did you have relatives
 or lodgers with you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
No, the - the - two - two bedrooms and like downstairs and that - now that now - listen to this one. When I were in Scowcroft Street there were lady called Mrs Pendlebury and she had two gathered breasts and do you know what so
mebody did? They boiled a couple of basins and put them on. Do you - imagine that now. It - well I mean - it's be - crucify you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What happened eventually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well - it cured her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 It brought the poison out you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes. Now - a fellow ca
lled Ike Broxup as used the - in the farm business, on farms and that, and I told him about it, he says, I could - I could - I could have drawn - drawn - them out a lot easier than that Joe, only, he says, it would have been a mucky job. I said, why what 
w
ould it be? He said, cow clap. Yes, cow clap. Now he says, put that on and it's - it's drawing powers. Now - what about that. Now for instance - when I were a boy like other boys and girls used to have pimples and blotches on your face. And they used to s
ell blood purifiers didn't they. Now what do you think - I didn't have Wincarnis, Halls wine or any of them. What did I take. I took just enough for to cover sixpence - in milk - gun powder. Yes. Gunpowder. Now - gunpowder, it's }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 composed}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  of five things. Ingredients. But - I can only think of four so somebody'll have to find out which is fifth if they want it. }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 It's sulphur - flowers of sulphur, brimstone, potash, saltpetre and another one. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 There were five. And they're best blood purifiers you'll get.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You never blow up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
No. No. it musn't have done me any harm, I'm eighty-one. Yes, it were better than all them lines as they were selling. No. So I mean to say they can look it up but there's five ingredients that - it's such a while since I've - I can't
 think of t'other one but fancy, you used to have brimstone and treacle didn't you. And they used to have flowers of sulphur didn't you. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 
Now saltpetre, you haven't - you don't use that as much as you use them others because that's for the water. So you don't use saltpetre to a big extent. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
There's another one besides, and honestly, that is the best blood purifier but - I daresay they wouldn't have it, it's no good now. But that's I used to - and then like - you know when you used to have - your throat used t
o get as you could hardly swallow. Yes. Well - the tonsils really had got - a white covering - white covering, it built up and made it - narrower.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You're thinking of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 diphtheria}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well, no, it's - oh no, it's just a sore throat and you can hardly 
swallow. This - 'cos your whatsname - tonsils - are covered with - covered white. So now, to - to cut that off you get - a tablespoonful of vinegar and with this - and tablespoon full of - black treacle. Now you have to warm your black treacle, you unders
tand that, for get it runny, else you can't mix it can you. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 So - gets this tablespoonful of black treacle and gets it hot, you know, and gets it moving. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Then I puts a spoon - tablespoonful of butter in, mixes that in, then I put a tablespoonful of vinegar i
n, does that. Now - if I'd wanted to sip vinegar - and just - vinegar I say it would have done just the same thing but I put these others for make it more palatable. Now I got the spoonful of black }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 treacle}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 , spoonful of butter, spoonful of vinegar, malt vin
egar. That acetic stuff. I mix 'em all up. Now I just sips that now and that vinegar as is in them other two cuts the white away.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Tell me about when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 , what sort of a husband were you, did you help your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well - no, I didn't help her so much because I worked at Farnworth and I'm going, we'll say, off at - start at eight o'clock and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You were still at the Co-op?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes. And - I don't know whether we worked 'til six o'clock or half past six or seven o'clock, I couldn't just tell you. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 So you worked long hours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 You never had any children did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did she do her own washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 She didn't make clothes or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh no, no, she didn't, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you ever repair shoes when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh yes, I had a last and that, you see, used to repair me shoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you do decorating or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh - well - just ordinary decorating. But - but see we were paying 
rent so naturally - yes. Yes, so we expected land - th'agent looked at decorating.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What was your landlord like, did you ever meet him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No. No, never met him. Met th'agent. I mean - he were - he were very good, you know what I mean, he - th'hous
e were in a pretty good shape. I mean, you can't take more out of th'house than what you paid in can you. I mean, these - these other people can't put the money down on a house for you and they lose it can they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How did you go on for meals when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 , did your wife get up with you for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No. We'd - me mother had trained us - that was me step-brothers too - that when we got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 
Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  she wouldn't be able - they weren't getting up for getting our breakfasts. We had to get our own b
reakfasts ready. And she didn't mind what we did on tablecloth. Whether we spilt our bacon fat, spilt tea or what, when we used to finish sometimes from table going our way, we had lumps of paper up here, lumps of paper up there where we spilt our fat and
 whatsname, but she never - never grumbled. But she would not get up for make our breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 So you never made your wife get up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you come home for your dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No, no. No, I used to have it out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How did you go on for food in those days, was your wife a good cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes. Well she were a good cook because I mean - I saw that she went to - you know, to classes. Oh yes, yes, yes. Like -;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How did she cook, did she have a range or did she have gas now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No - ordinary - ordinary oven. They'd ovens then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No gas cooker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No, no, no. No, they had the fire there and - t'oven here. I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14436562\charrsid9517149 mean,}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  them were all right in wintertime you know. You used get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 thumb plate}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  now in wintertime when it were nice and hot, wrap it up in a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 blanket}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
 and put it in bed and used lie on it. Oh yes. Yes, that - used - you got thumbplates for that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 When you got up on your own what did you have for breakfast, did you still cook bacon and egg when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 On your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
Yes. Yes. Aye, that's right - well it just depends what you feel like, see, you might feel like - bit of grapefruit for kick off with, you know, or you might want toast and a poached egg. It just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What about your teas, you had your lunches at work didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes, well - tea - just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you take sandwiches?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 That's right, you used to take sandwiches and working }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 at}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  Co-op they always supplied you with tea and sugar, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 And then you came home to a cooked meal at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What were your favourite meals and what did she cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Yes, so - well - she could do all kinds of different things you know but I used like my tea very strong and I didn't like milk. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 And soda were in same colour of a bag as su
gar so I brews my tea and not bothering this 'ere soda must have broken gone to bits like, like sugar does, just like that and puts it in and stirs it up and - I thought, this tea's nice and strong. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well I always drinks after I've had something to eat, I don't - wash it down - have it after. So I goes and gets a right cup - oh it's right slimey, the taste is - I'd put soda in. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What kind of dinners did she cook you at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well like - well I liked potato pie. Yes. And then I used like - chi
ps and cheese. Yes. You know cheese - but - I used to like that - that Lancashire cheese - that breaking cheese and I used like it be done in milk so that it wouldn't - set like as you'd stretch it, you get me?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 What about weekends when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 , did you have a joint now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
Oh yes, that's right, yes. Yes, I used to have - sometimes you'd get a - part of leg like, like a small leg you know. And sometimes you'd get a bit of beef like, bit of rump steak or brisket, you know, something like that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did she make her own bread or pickles or jam or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well - well - well she did now and again but - she hadn't all that time but she could make some very good cakes. Aye, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did she ever bottle fruit or make pickles or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 She - sometimes she would do you know. I remember - what's that - tar - tar sommat, it makes it yellow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Cream of tartar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 No, it weren't cream of tarter - tar - taranta - taran salt. It - no, it weren't cream of tartar as
 made it yellow - that yellow, for - for - for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 piccalilli}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
, it's a - a funny name. It starts off with tartar summat. Oh yes, and then like - have a - a crab apple tree guarding. I've lost two thirds of it but still - it's here, plenty of crab - crab apples 
on. She used to make crab apple jelly but - not worth it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you grow your own vegetables or keep livestock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh no, we had - we had no garden. No. I mean say, it's not worth the trouble making crab apple jelly and it's not worth the trouble mak
ing damson jam, 'cos when she used to make damson jam she used to always want all stones out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 And you had to pick them out did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Well there - there - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15296863\charrsid9517149 there seemed}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149  more stones than jam when you made damson jam you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 After you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 
 how many times a week would you eat met?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Oh yes, yes, yes, yes, there were more meat - meat eaters then. Well I mean, meat were cheap.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 How many times a week would you eat it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2235835 JW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 I should say - we'd have it three times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1250662 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9849632\charrsid9517149 Did you ever have tinned meat after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2893269 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
